title: Headmistress fiora and mundo mundo skin
body: Hi, so I contacted support about this issue and was told that I should bring it here as well, I own the headmistress fiora and mundo mundo skin, however when I look at them on my account they do not display, but I am able to select and load them in champion select, just not from my account screen. Seems like a display bug since its not showing up in my account screen, but I can select and play as them in champion select

replies.body:
Hey Rakhanddon,

Thanks for the report! We're aware of an issue with content not displaying in the Champion Details page and are working on a fix. This won't affect your ability to use these skins. :]

**EDIT**: This should be resolved!
